sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant R as Record (JSONL)
    participant G as LangGraph
    participant C as Context node
    participant L as LLM node
    participant API as Gemini (via gateway)
    participant P as Parse + Compliance
    participant E as Evaluate

    Note over G: deadline = now + TOTAL_LLM_BUDGET_S (1.8s)

    R->>G: invoke
    G->>G: intake → safety (validate, consent, scan)
    alt no consent / unsafe / bad record
        G-->>R: ABORT (safe no-send + reasoning)
    else ok
        G->>C: build prompt
        C->>C: derive facts + rank few-shot (~2k tokens)
        C->>L: system + user prompt

        loop attempt 1..MAX_RETRIES (shared budget)
            Note over L: timeout = min(LLM_TIMEOUT_S 1.6, remaining budget)
            L->>API: generate (temp=0, JSON)
            alt responds in time
                API-->>L: raw JSON
                L->>P: output
                P->>P: extract JSON, validate schema,<br/>re-impose LEGAL guardrails only
                alt valid
                    P->>E: success
                    E-->>R: EMIT (message + next_action + 23 AC scores)
                else malformed
                    P-->>L: RETRY with correction prompt
                end
            else timeout / budget exhausted / API error
                API--xL: (too slow)
                L-->>R: ABORT (LLM_TIMEOUT / BUDGET / ERROR)
            end
        end
    end

    Note over L,API: ⚠ On a slower machine, calls exceed 1.6s →<br/>timeout → ABORT → score drops.<br/>Fix: raise LLM_TIMEOUT_S / TOTAL_LLM_BUDGET_S
